{"Sid":0,"Did":18012,"Id":"282325","Title":"頭城忠孝新村天后宮捐題碑","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-24/de812ac9-6ecd-4a35-9c08-4dc121482062/collection/2dd162ff-93aa-46b2-a0a8-0af8ea883a7c/108-her-cw-1155-201910300009115db8638ad1d500.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-24/de812ac9-6ecd-4a35-9c08-4dc121482062/collection/2e8d7dca-ac23-4d6a-a8bd-6cb744155886/108-her-cw-1155-201910300009115db8638ad1d501.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Object","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n頭城忠孝新村天后宮為大陳移民聚落廟宇，廟內除供奉自大陳原鄉攜來之媽祖、呂祖大仙與三官佛神像為其特色。在廟內兩側牆面可見「謹將於天后宮屋頂重建經費樂助人方名金額列下」與「擴建本村天后宮宇經費樂助人方名金額列下」兩組以手繪彩磁書寫之捐題碑，在這兩組樂助人芳名碑中可以觀察到大陳人男性取名的一些特色，譬如名字中有「玉」、「奶」或「妹」的比例相當高，與台灣傳統男性命名的傳統有很大的差異。此外，亦可見此兩面樂助人芳名碑上方掛有孫中山與蔣中正遺像，也充分反映大陳移民對於當時國民政府領導者的高度認同。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.886634","Keyword_Latitude":"24.935827","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/object/B6987B5E-F8A5-4FE3-A28B-1C30A51B2AC4","Original_Identifier":"282325","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","alternativeHeadline":"","Keywords":"大陳 / 天后宮 / 忠孝新村 / 捐題碑 / 頭城","dates":"創作時間 / 民國/戰後時期","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 19:47:07","Creator":"不詳","publisher":"","mediaType":"有形文物","language":"","timelines":"","city":"宜蘭縣頭城鎮","address":"忠孝新村54號","lng":"121.886634","lat":"24.935827","contributors":"","contributor":"林世傑/ 蔡明志","size":"","admin":"","award":"","character":"","contentLocation":"","acquireWay":"","acquireSource":"","storage":"","version":"","isbn":"","onlineAuthLink":"","stuff":"","url":"","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","citation":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-24/de812ac9-6ecd-4a35-9c08-4dc121482062/collectionOpen/b75e9f72-5b00-4048-b41f-87f6a69ce015/108-her-cw-1155-re-201910300010215db8638ad1d500.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-24/de812ac9-6ecd-4a35-9c08-4dc121482062/collectionOpen/cdb93104-dc93-4ba0-aeb5-c5a14772495c/108-her-cw-1155-re-20191030001021